data.description: Beautifully wooded 5 acres with Large 4 or 5 bedroom Palm Harbor home! The wonderful countryside land is level & heavily treed. New exterior AC unit: September 2023! Office could be the 5th bedroom. Spacious Island Kitchen. Property is completely fenced and includes a 20x12 storeroom/workshop and a 20x11 covered patio.  Some upgrades (flooring and painting) have been recently done.  Tenants are a couple who have cared for the property and been there for several years.  Current loan is an FHA so it appears that the home has a permanent foundation and would continue to qualify for FHA/VA financing. Note: Seller will give allowance for carpet replacement.
